I'm forced to dock 4 stars now (took off another as it's still not fixed) due to the recent loss of swipe-between-pictures within a folder😫 (even though I'm using QuickPic which has this ability), and the loss of a convenient paste button right at the top of the screen.  Delving into menus to paste doesn't work for me.   Also a third problem: the app reverts to the home directory EVERY time the app is navigated away from, with NO setting to change this behavior.  (It used to remember where I was last and go back to that.)  This app has been very useful and nearly perfect over the years.  I hope I can say that again soon, but in the typical devil-could-care attitude app developers so often seem to have, I doubt it.  I'll be looking for a new file browser.
